name: Premium "Cartel Living" Varsity Jacket Style #2
description:
All of our jackets feature rich wools and genuine cowhide leathers in a wide variety of colors and styles featuring a leather trimmed inside cell/wallet pocket. 

-This Classic Varsity Jacket features a full wool body 
-Genuine European Leather sleeves
-High quality constructed snap button style 
-Knit pattern stripe detail on sleeves and pocket trim 
-Classic Athletic  hand sewn Lettering 
Sizes 
-*Personalized Name on right chest of your choice
-*"Cartel Living " "Secret Society" Written on back of Jacket in Script Hand Sewn Lettering 
-All lettering is custom made using the finest FELT fabric available.
-Sizes run from Extra Small-6X (Tall option available in all sizes for $20 more)
-Email us for color request for availability 


 ****All custom made jackets 'WITH OR WITHOUT LETTERING' ship from our offices in 6-8 weeks.
Rush Delivery available for 25% of cost for faster delivery. 
 
 RETURNS / EXCHANGES / OUT OF STOCK ITEMS
 
 *CUSTOM JACKETS AND DECORATED JACKETS ARE NOT RETURNABLE

- If decorated jackets have been incorrectly/improperly personalized, our Customer Support Team must be notified immediately so that appropriate adjustments or corrective action can be taken.
 - Worn or altered garments are not returnable. Therefore, it's especially important that jackets are inspected upon receipt.
 - Please call us prior to returning/exchanging an item. We will give you a return-authorization number to ensure that your return/exchange is accepted.
